      WESTERN WEAR – CHIC AND CURRENT

      We have all wished for a wardrobe miracle on those especially hard days when we have absolutely no time or energy to expend on our outfits. Sure, our favourite celebrities have an entire entourage to make them look the way they do but there really is no need to spend big bucks to get your sartorial game on fleek. Besides, even the most clued-in of fashionistas have had to face moments of despair, when they thought that their outfit just did not make the cut.

      We at Myntra know that you have chosen us to be your style guardians for a reason – this time around, we help you keep up with the ever-changing dynamics of the fashion scene with our all-new western wear collection. Choose from the biggest brands, including Forever 21, Roadster, FabAlley, Mango, Dressberry, United Colors of Benetton, All About You, Mast & Harbour, Ajile by Pantaloons, Alan Solly Woman, Biba, Bombay High, and so many more. It’s time to pull your socks up and style up like a star – shop for western wear online on Myntra before your favourite pieces are all sold out.

      INSPIRING NEW LOOKS

      The thing about fresh fashion is that it automatically inspires the wearer and spawns newer, bolder, chicer looks. Our western wear collection boasts of tops, dresses, T-shirts, shirts, jeans, skirts, trousers, jackets, dungarees, coats, capris, jumpsuits, jeggings, track pants, suits, and pretty much everything else you could possibly want. Choose the best fit for yourself by sifting through western wear items based on size and fabric, colour and print, styling details and brand, fit and budget, etc. There are various filters in place just to help you do that, all in a matter of minutes (express shopping, anyone).

      Our western wear online range has all that you need to take care of your daily sartorial needs. Kicked to be going on a Hawaiian beach holiday with your beau? Pick a floral printed multi-coloured mini skirt – pair it with a colour-pop sleeveless top and flip-flops for a lively yet practical look. Want to channel your inner goth chick? Choose a black and grey, fitted jacket – wear it over a black or navy-blue graphic print tee, distressed denims and black leather boots for a look that means business. Be the picture of elegance in a beige and black lace detail maxi dress – this western wear item is all you need to woo your man on a romantic dinner date.

      VARIETY, VARIETY AND MORE VARIETY

      Who does not like a good denim-on-denim look! Pair a three-fourth sleeve washed blue denim shirt with a pair of dark navy-blue jeans and sneakers for a fun look for when you are heading out to meet your gal pals. Pick a pencil skirt in black, blue or grey to wear to work with a pinstriped formal blouse and cat-eye framed glasses. Do not forget to pick up a few pairs of solid colour track pants from our western wear range – they will come in handy when you hit the gym or go jogging every morning.
